  • Classes in interfaces used by actionKeywords 
    Class and Description
    IAfterAction
    IAfterAction is a way to perform an Action Keywords a given number of times until the expected outcome is achieved.
    IKeyword
    The IKeyword interface is the base model for all of the Framework Selenium Keywords.
    ILogging
    Primary interface used for Logging within the framework Logging is designed to use an interface so that any type of logging library can be used without issues of refactoring.
    IWait
    Framework provided Wait Keywords Wait Keywords are any keyword intended delay the execution of Selenium until some specific condition is met.

  • Classes in interfaces used by data 
    Class and Description
    ITestCase
    Model used by the framework to allow for various types of Non-coded test design like Excel spreadsheets and JSON files This Interface models a Test Case and includes methods for getting information about a Test Case
    ITestRunner
    Primary interface model for executing ITestCase implementations This Interface will run Framework Keywords, Custom created Keywords, and Page Object methods
    ITestStep
    Model used by the framework to allow for various types of Non-coded test design like Excel spreadsheets and JSON files This interface models a single test step as part of an ITestCase.
